<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/platform4> <http://ogp.me/ns#title> "Platform4"@en .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/platform4> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Platform4 is a wholly owned subsidiary of Network Rail, established to lead the regeneration of surplus railway land across the UK. Platform4 transforms brownfield rail-led land across the country to deliver well-connected homes, communities, industrial sites and workspaces. Platform4 is a public corporation of the Network Rail and the Department for Transport ."@en .
